1
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:15,900
[My Everlasting Bride]

2
00:00:16,020 --> 00:00:18,860
[You're the reason I keep going.]

3
00:00:19,140 --> 00:00:21,100
[Episode 20]

4
00:00:21,100 --> 00:00:22,340
[Jiangzhou Hu Residence]

5
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:24,100
Xiaodie.

6
00:00:24,100 --> 00:00:26,220
Looks like you've suffered outside.

7
00:00:27,060 --> 00:00:28,420
I missed you so much.

8
00:00:31,470 --> 00:00:32,740
I'm back now.

9
00:00:32,740 --> 00:00:33,950
I'm glad you're back.

10
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:55,990
Nie Zhen is not dead.

11
00:00:57,310 --> 00:00:59,590
He has his own plans.

12
00:00:59,590 --> 00:01:00,460
Right?

13
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:08,950
Young Marshal.

14
00:01:09,380 --> 00:01:10,340
Liu Xiu.

15
00:01:10,710 --> 00:01:12,340
Do you believe in fate?

16
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:14,100
It doesn't matter
whether I believe in it or not.

17
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:15,950
But I believe more
in taking matters into our own hands.

18
00:01:17,670 --> 00:01:18,590
Young Marshal.

19
00:01:18,900 --> 00:01:20,100
You really want
to take a chance like that?

20
00:01:25,710 --> 00:01:27,900
Put a bullet into the magazine,

21
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,430
lock it with your thumb,

22
00:01:29,430 --> 00:01:31,150
and rotate it with a force of 12 newtons.

23
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:33,790
Two seconds later, it's loaded.

24
00:01:34,510 --> 00:01:35,710
The magazine at this moment

25
00:01:35,710 --> 00:01:36,790
must be the one you preselected.

26
00:01:36,790 --> 00:01:38,870
Although the chances seem
to be one in six,

27
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:40,540
in reality,

28
00:01:41,230 --> 00:01:42,430
it's 100 percent.

29
00:01:46,070 --> 00:01:47,150
I never take risks.

30
00:01:48,030 --> 00:01:49,710
I only use the information gap to win.

31
00:01:49,980 --> 00:01:51,950
So you're right

32
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:52,710
about taking matters into our own hands.

33
00:01:53,430 --> 00:01:55,510
So you know how to use a gun?

34
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,430
How come I didn't know that?

35
00:01:58,380 --> 00:02:01,340
I don't like guns,
but I know how to use them.

36
00:02:02,180 --> 00:02:03,980
What I need is information.

37
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:06,740
That's all we have.

38
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:12,340
- The thing I entrusted you...
- Don't worry, Young Marshal.

39
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:14,550
I'll protect Young Madam with my life.

40
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:16,110
Be sure to make it.

41
00:02:16,110 --> 00:02:16,430
Yes!

42
00:02:21,390 --> 00:02:22,310
Say something!

43
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:24,660
Young Marshal

44
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:26,940
will be fine.

45
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,390
Liu Xiu.

46
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:30,900
Is this how you protect him?

47
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:31,780
But as you know, orders are orders.

48
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:34,180
He ordered me to protect you.

49
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:37,500
Isn't it all the same?

50
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,460
Isn't it the same

51
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,220
as putting himself in a dead end?

52
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,060
I'm sure Young Marshal

53
00:02:45,780 --> 00:02:47,110
will survive.

54
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:56,740
[Yuzhou Prison]

55
00:02:57,180 --> 00:02:58,430
I'll give you one last chance.

56
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,620
Tell me who you are.

57
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:05,460
I really escaped from Jiangzhou.

58
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:08,150
I worked as a jeweler

59
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,620
for the Hu family in Jiangzhou.

60
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:11,590
No matter how many times you ask,

61
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:13,660
that's my only answer.

62
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:15,310
Then why did you come to Yuzhou?

63
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:19,870
Let me tell you the truth.

64
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,740
I owed a lot of debts.

65
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:26,180
But when I ran away,

66
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:27,740
I brought a lot of jewelry with me.

67
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:29,940
If you're willing

68
00:03:29,940 --> 00:03:31,180
to spare my life,

69
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,900
I'll give you half of it.

70
00:03:34,180 --> 00:03:35,620
Are you trying to bribe me

71
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:37,030
with these little benefits?

72
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:38,710
All of it.

73
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:40,870
I can give you all of it.

74
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:42,780
As long as you spare my life,

75
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:45,030
I'll work for you.

76
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:47,740
Can we make a deal?

77
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:51,420
♪Loneliness sealed away♪

78
00:03:52,990 --> 00:03:53,830
(Nie Zhen.)

79
00:03:54,830 --> 00:03:56,430
(I know you're still alive)

80
00:03:57,830 --> 00:04:00,550
(and working on a dangerous plan.)

81
00:04:02,620 --> 00:04:04,180
(I write in my diary.)

82
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,710
(Unsure where to send it)

83
00:04:07,660 --> 00:04:09,430
(and when)

84
00:04:09,990 --> 00:04:11,390
(it will reach you.)

85
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:15,460
(But I know that day will come.)

86
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:18,420
(This is what you promised me.)

87
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:22,620
♪Fear not when love runs over♪

88
00:04:23,140 --> 00:04:26,820
♪Loved too much turns the heart a demon♪

89
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:31,190
(I've arrived at the Hu family.)

90
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:33,750
(I've met with my father)

91
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,390
(and got settled.)

92
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:38,630
(Liu Xiu is in charge of my safety.)

93
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:41,950
(I know why you left)

94
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:43,190
(the most trusted guy with me.)

95
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:45,980
(I'll make you feel at ease.)

96
00:04:47,980 --> 00:04:49,710
(Everything is fine in the Hu family.)

97
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:51,860
(I'm waiting for you)

98
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:54,070
(to come back and be with me.)

99
00:04:54,900 --> 00:04:59,060
♪Letting go of what has not left♪

100
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:00,460
♪Unpersuadable♪

101
00:05:02,150 --> 00:05:03,030
I really don't know

102
00:05:03,030 --> 00:05:04,220
about Nie Zhen's plan.

103
00:05:05,590 --> 00:05:07,300
I have plenty of time

104
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:08,460
to wait for you to tell me.

105
00:05:09,590 --> 00:05:12,540
I've said everything I know.

106
00:05:14,590 --> 00:05:16,540
Why do you always favor her?

107
00:05:16,590 --> 00:05:19,220
I've witnessed what she's done.

108
00:05:20,590 --> 00:05:22,340
You may have witnessed it.

109
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:24,300
But I experienced it firsthand.

110
00:05:24,540 --> 00:05:26,150
She called me out of the Shen family

111
00:05:26,150 --> 00:05:27,590
with the purpose of killing Nie Zhen.

112
00:05:27,980 --> 00:05:29,780
She already had a clue back then.

113
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:32,300
I held a gun against Young Marshal.

114
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:35,070
If she really got into Nie Manor
in order to harm you,

115
00:05:35,070 --> 00:05:36,950
what's the point of killing Nie Zhen?

116
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:39,780
It's just a cover-up.

117
00:05:40,150 --> 00:05:41,030
Sis.

118
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:42,660
You're truly confused, aren't you?

119
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:44,660
She thought you were dead.

120
00:05:45,150 --> 00:05:46,780
Who's she trying to fool?

121
00:05:50,780 --> 00:05:51,590
Sis.

122
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:53,660
I have a feeling

123
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,780
that everything is gonna end soon.

124
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:59,540
Xiaodie won't come back to save you.

125
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,220
It's not her.

126
00:06:02,660 --> 00:06:04,780
There's someone else who cares about you?

127
00:06:05,150 --> 00:06:06,150
It's Young Marshal.

128
00:06:06,460 --> 00:06:07,220
Ha!

129
00:06:08,460 --> 00:06:10,660
You're praying for a dead man

130
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:12,030
to save you?

131
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:15,780
Didn't you die once before as well?

132
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:17,830
Also in the river.

133
00:06:43,580 --> 00:06:46,220
♪Dreams sifting through the fingers♪

134
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:49,460
♪With so many stories left unfinished♪

135
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:53,900
♪Drifting towards who,
turning and tossing♪

136
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:57,220
♪Long ago and so far away♪

137
00:06:58,900 --> 00:07:01,580
♪Waiting, oh, for rebirth through Nirvana♪

138
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:04,780
♪The Milky Way's stars passed too hastily♪

139
00:07:06,540 --> 00:07:09,220
♪Still clinging to those eyes♪

140
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:12,100
♪A gust of wind through the brambles♪

141
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:16,140
♪Unwilling to resign
the rest of my life to fate♪

142
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:17,740
♪Wading through endless seas of blood♪

143
00:07:17,740 --> 00:07:19,260
♪Obsession♪

144
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:21,140
♪Surging♪

145
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:23,660
♪Vainly hoping in the crevices of time♪

146
00:07:23,980 --> 00:07:28,260
♪Never ceasing, learning to be composed♪

147
00:07:28,700 --> 00:07:32,180
♪Loneliness cherishes
the afterglow of the setting sun♪

148
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:36,260
♪In rumors, where did she come and go?♪

149
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:38,780
♪As always, ice and snow melt♪

150
00:07:39,220 --> 00:07:43,820
♪How did I fall into a silent void?♪

151
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:47,860
♪Eyes empty yet unrepentant♪

152
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:51,700
♪Concealing boundless solitary courage♪

153
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:53,580
♪Devoting half a lifetime♪

154
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:55,220
♪Indulging in♪

155
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:58,940
♪Life and death together♪

156
00:07:59,340 --> 00:08:02,820
♪Loneliness wastes
the afterglow of the setting sun♪

157
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:06,940
♪In tales, with whom
did she once embrace?♪

158
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:09,540
♪Vulgar folks chat and laugh merrily♪

159
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:14,620
♪How did I disappoint sincere affection?♪

160
00:08:14,820 --> 00:08:18,500
♪A thought insincere amidst the dust♪

161
00:08:18,740 --> 00:08:22,340
♪She won't avoid
her destined ordeal in this life♪

162
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:24,220
♪Not destined to encounter♪

163
00:08:24,420 --> 00:08:25,860
♪Yet firmly believing♪

164
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:29,780
♪Life and death together♪

